TI  - Randomized Crossover Clinical Trial of Nicotinamide Riboside and Coenzyme Q10 on  Metabolic Health and Mitochondrial Bioenergetics in CKD.
AU  - Ahmadi A
AU  - Valencia AP
AU  - Begue G
AU  - Norman JE
